section_text: 1 1 This Act may be cited as the Parks Regulation (Amendment) Act 1974. 2 The  Parks Regulation Act 1872 and the  Parks Regulation (Amendment) Act 1926 and this Act may be cited together as the Parks Regulation Acts 1872 to 1974.
2 The Parks Regulation Act 1872 shall have effect subject to the amendments set out in the Schedule to this Act.
